    <item>
      <title>据 Puck 报道，大卫·鲁宾斯坦领导的集团将收购美国职业棒球大联盟金莺队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/david-rubenstein-group-in-deal-to-buy-mlb-s-orioles-puck-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，凯雷集团联合创始人大卫·鲁宾斯坦 (David Rubenstein) 和一个投资者财团同意以 17.3 亿美元的价格从安杰洛斯家族手中收购巴尔的摩金莺棒球队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/david-rubenstein-group-in-deal-to-buy-mlb-s-orioles-puck-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 23:51:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲美元债券销售创 2016 年以来最差开局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/dollar-bond-sales-in-asia-see-worst-start-to-year-since-2016</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着地区借款人在国内筹集更便宜的资金并等待美联储降息，亚洲的美元债券销售迎来了八年来最疲软的开局，与强劲的全球趋势相反。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/dollar-bond-sales-in-asia-see-worst-start-to-year-since-2016</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市低迷，日本债券因日本央行押注而下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
